.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-ROUTE-HINTS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-route-hints \- extract routing hints from a BOLT-11 invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-route-hints
.I bolt11
.SH DESCRIPTION
Decodes the BOLT-11 invoice and returns any embedded routing hints
from the
.B r
field.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable or the invoice is invalid.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"route_hint_count":N,"hints":[...]}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1),
.BR lightning-route-find (1)
